[
    {
        "text": "Do four-day weeks work?",
        "startTime": 858,
        "endTime": 2945,
        "slowStartTime": 1437,
        "slowEndTime": 4643
    },
    {
        "text": "When French company boss Laurent de la Clergerie...",
        "startTime": 3723,
        "endTime": 6417,
        "slowStartTime": 5734,
        "slowEndTime": 9851
    },
    {
        "text": "...decided to let his staff work a four-day week...",
        "startTime": 6496,
        "endTime": 9389,
        "slowStartTime": 9894,
        "slowEndTime": 14308
    },
    {
        "text": "...on the same pay as before,...",
        "startTime": 9690,
        "endTime": 11415,
        "slowStartTime": 14685,
        "slowEndTime": 17348
    },
    {
        "text": "...some people took him for a crazy person.",
        "startTime": 11805,
        "endTime": 14398,
        "slowStartTime": 17858,
        "slowEndTime": 21822
    },
    {
        "text": "But a year on, his LDLC company selling consumer technology...",
        "startTime": 15103,
        "endTime": 19664,
        "slowStartTime": 22804,
        "slowEndTime": 29721
    },
    {
        "text": "...has increased annual turnover by 40 percent...",
        "startTime": 19963,
        "endTime": 23427,
        "slowStartTime": 30094,
        "slowEndTime": 35365
    },
    {
        "text": "...without hiring any extra staff.",
        "startTime": 23804,
        "endTime": 26007,
        "slowStartTime": 35856,
        "slowEndTime": 39236
    },
    {
        "text": "As the world emerges from a global health crisis...",
        "startTime": 26701,
        "endTime": 29803,
        "slowStartTime": 40202,
        "slowEndTime": 44929
    },
    {
        "text": "...that prompted many people to reevaluate their work-life balance,...",
        "startTime": 29983,
        "endTime": 33733,
        "slowStartTime": 45125,
        "slowEndTime": 50824
    },
    {
        "text": "...companies and workers around the world are asking an important question.",
        "startTime": 34110,
        "endTime": 38121,
        "slowStartTime": 51315,
        "slowEndTime": 57406
    },
    {
        "text": "Can they work less?",
        "startTime": 38453,
        "endTime": 39616,
        "slowStartTime": 57830,
        "slowEndTime": 59649
    },
    {
        "text": "De la Clergerie says before he embarked on the change,...",
        "startTime": 41793,
        "endTime": 45102,
        "slowStartTime": 62839,
        "slowEndTime": 67878
    },
    {
        "text": "...he did the math.",
        "startTime": 45372,
        "endTime": 46295,
        "slowStartTime": 68208,
        "slowEndTime": 69668
    },
    {
        "text": "LDLC employs approximately 1,000 people.",
        "startTime": 46571,
        "endTime": 50197,
        "slowStartTime": 70007,
        "slowEndTime": 75520
    },
    {
        "text": "He worked out that even in the worst-case scenario,...",
        "startTime": 50892,
        "endTime": 53388,
        "slowStartTime": 76488,
        "slowEndTime": 80307
    },
    {
        "text": "...the change would add to labor costs by at most 1.6 million dollars per year.",
        "startTime": 53523,
        "endTime": 58633,
        "slowStartTime": 80434,
        "slowEndTime": 88175
    },
    {
        "text": "It was a manageable risk he was willing to take.",
        "startTime": 59194,
        "endTime": 62019,
        "slowStartTime": 88941,
        "slowEndTime": 93254
    },
    {
        "text": "Since then, he said that absenteeism and sick leaves have gone down.",
        "startTime": 62175,
        "endTime": 66287,
        "slowStartTime": 93412,
        "slowEndTime": 99655
    },
    {
        "text": "The company has also not had to hire new people...",
        "startTime": 66493,
        "endTime": 68970,
        "slowStartTime": 99890,
        "slowEndTime": 103680
    },
    {
        "text": "...to offset the reduction in hours worked.",
        "startTime": 69037,
        "endTime": 71149,
        "slowStartTime": 103706,
        "slowEndTime": 106949
    },
    {
        "text": "And although the four-day week is not the only factor,...",
        "startTime": 71629,
        "endTime": 74914,
        "slowStartTime": 107593,
        "slowEndTime": 112596
    },
    {
        "text": "...De la Clergerie says it contributed to a jump in turnover...",
        "startTime": 75407,
        "endTime": 79165,
        "slowStartTime": 113261,
        "slowEndTime": 118972
    },
    {
        "text": "...from around 550 million dollars before the change to nearly 770 million dollars.",
        "startTime": 79388,
        "endTime": 86852,
        "slowStartTime": 119232,
        "slowEndTime": 130503
    }
]